specially important in view of the need to develop and apply conservation-oriented programs tomaintain biodiversity. A review of recent improvements in techniques for inventorying bats shows that a combination of methods, including mistnetting and acoustic monitoring, ismandatory for such studies.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Kalko, Elisabeth K. V.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jr., Charles O. Handley", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/c8254e7232debb300b8d7794bb6149a8", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/a8a427c017005f5f42a4837b7f40f3e1fc75eb11099f0afccb40ca30d842d2d4", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/V6TKIIND", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/V6TKIIND", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/1748c90eba85298cde80837e72c1b641!/b61800-64261", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1/2,", "pages": "319-333", "title": "Plant Ecology", "volume": "153"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/c8254e7232debb300b8d7794bb6149a8"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:V6TKIIND"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "